# Project: Quote-to-Order AI Agent

## Stack
- Language: Python 3.10+
- UI: Streamlit
- AI Brain: Gemini API (google-generativeai)
- Data: Local CSV files only (no external database)

## Rules
1. No new libraries without approval
2. Keep code simple and modular
3. One file = one responsibility
4. Never break working code
5. If unclear, ask before implementing